messages.message: hey everyone - if you were running webpack locally and encountering some `JavaScript heap out of memory` errors, John St (not tagging him so I donâ€™t wake him up on vacation :face_with_finger_covering_closed_lips:) has put in a workaround for this. you can now customize what gets built by webpack by creating an `.ib-dev.json` file in the `/webpacked` directory. you can read more about it here (https://github.com/instabase/frontend-docs/blob/master/local.md#webpack); please thread or DM me if you have questions!
